projects.name: Housing data Analysis on metropolitan cities
projects.description: Gained hands-on experience in data analysis with Python to extract insights and visualize effectively. Worked on projects involving data collection, preprocessing, visualization, and analysis. Developed proficiency in Python programming and utilized libraries such as Pandas, NumPy, and Matplotlib for data manipulation and visualization.

projects.name: Sequence Prediction using Deep-Learning technique
projects.description: Developed an LSTM-based deep learning model to predict the next block ID in file sequences within a distributed file system, using synthetic log data of 100,000 entries. Implemented extensive preprocessing techniques including text-to-CSV conversion, categorical variable encoding, and frequency column addition to enhance data quality. Achieved 86.53 percent accuracy, 0.99 precision, and 0.85 recall, showcasing the models effectiveness in capturing long-range dependencies and complex patterns in sequence prediction tasks.
